ctags list all tags kinds of a language: ctags --list-kinds-full=<lang>
ctags list tags kinds of a language with specified kinds: ctags --kinds-<kinds-lang>=<kinds> --list-kinds-full=<list-kind-lang>
ctags recurse into directories and output tags file with default kinds: ctags -R <path>
ctags recurse into directories and output tags file with specified kinds: ctags --kinds-<kinds-lang>=<kinds> -R <path>
